name: Daniel Rey Cimafranca
text: Clogged nozzles. Probably old stock. As suggested try to complain at atore where you bought it. You might have to make a scene, eg wag kayo bibili dito defective cartriges nila!, cause they will claim its a consumable thus not subject to warranty ü
